     C                     ENDSR
     C*
**  MSG (ERROR MESSAGE)
E-01 MUST INPUT < 0.1.2.3 > FOR UPDATE INSTRUCTION
E-02 NOT INPUT INTRAL COMPANY PRT NUMBER
E-03 CAN'T INPUT TARGET PART NBR WHEN UPDATE INST ISN'T ADDED
E-04 NO APPLICABLE DATA YOU WILL CANCEL IN DIE ALLOTMENT M/F
E-05 ALREADY CANCEL DIE ALLOTMENT M/F THOUGH YOU WILL CANCEL
E-06 NO APPLICABLE DATA YOU WILL CHANGE IN DIE ALLOTMENT M/F
E-07 ALREADY CANCEL DIE ALLOTMENT M/F THOUGH YOU WILL CHANGE
E-08 IT'D ALREADY ADDED DIE ALLOTMENT M/F THOUGH YOU'LL ADD
E-09 YOU CAN NOT INQUERY THE DATA NOT IN DIE ALLOTMENT M/F
